In theory spirit modulates sound to speak no matter the method. The boxes sweep tuning does the same thing as a manual sweep tuning its all just scanning across the band. Some find it easier to have it done automatically for them. Depends on personal preference =)

Best I can say to anyone is try whats available to you.

Misty



